Anubis/Hades/Unitron/Nemesis Enforcer/Ramhorn:




Anubis, Hades, and Unitron saw Oblitertron and then Radistor go back into 
their teams.  The large part of the battle over, all three of the Newcomers 
headed back for base.

---

Nemesis Enforcer raised his rifle, firing off ten rapid laser blasts off at 
Prowl's back, hovering in the air.

---

Ramhorn had lost the other Predacons, and approached the Ark slowly.
